overview.en: Participants of the Ocean Global platform interact with each other within a global ecosystem. Ocean Token (BKB) is a means of creating economic incentives to reward platform members. BKB acts as the main component enabling Ocean Global Consensus between participants.
overview.zh: Ocean Global 平台参与者在全局生态系统中相互交互。Ocean Token (BKB) 是创建经济激励以奖励平台成员的手段。BKB 作为主要组件，在参与者之间实现 Ocean Global 共识。
